quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Toto biabura ebise ebirambi khumundu, olwa yaali naalali eshindu shirumbulwa tawe."
  76,2,"Toto efwe khwaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende imwo yobulamu, yesasania, (yomusatsa nende omukhasi) khulwokhumutema, kho nikhumukholaye okhuwulila muno, nende okhulola po."
  76,3,"Toto efwe khwamulunjisia kunjira ilunjifu, niyenya asubire Nyasaye mana abe wokhupa orio, nohomba alonde khunjira ya obukhayi (alobe injira ya Nyasaye)."
  76,4,"Toto efwe khwarecheshela Abakhayi eminyororo, nende tsirimba nende omulilo omululu."
  76,5,"Toto Abandu abalayi balinywa eshinywebwa shiasasibwamwo ‘kafura’."
  76,6,"Ne Isebele ya Abandu ba Nyasaye balinywamwo, bali ikhola ikhulukusie mubunji."
  76,7,"Bakholanga kabalaka, ne baritsanga inyanga yobusiro bwayio buliswana."
  76,8,"Ne balisinjia eshilibwa shia abene bashiyanza Abamanani, nende Abafwilwa nende Ababoye."
  76,9,"“Toto efwe khubalisinjia khulwokhwenya obweni bwa Nyasaye, shikhubenyakhwo omurungo nohomba orio muno tawe."
  76,10,"Toto efwe khuritsaanga okhurulana khu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, inyanga yobutinyu nende Omusando.”"
  76,11,"Kho mana Nyasaye alibashinga okhurulana nende obusiro bwe inyanga eyo, ne alibakhola okhulolekha obulayi po, khandi abasangafu."
  76,12,"Ne alibarunga omukunda kwomwikulu nende tsingubo tsieshironyo, khulwa okhwifwila khwabu."
  76,13,"Omo baliyekha khubisaala bioluyali, shibalilolamwo omubasu omululu nohomba omunyiri omululu tawe."
  76,14,"Ne ebiinikha biliba ahambi ninabo, ne ebiamo biamwo bilieletsanga muno."
  76,15,"Ne balitendelwa khubindu bie ifedha nende bikombe bia tsigilasi."
  76,16,"Tsihilasi tsia ifedha inzwenufu shinga shiwoo, tsiachelwa khushichelo."
  76,17,"Ne omo balinywesibwamwo eshinywebwa shasasibwamwo itangawizi."
  76,18,"Eyo isebele iliyo ilangwa mbu Salsabil."
  76,19,"Ne balibetsela luno nende lulia okhubatenda abasiani bashili ababukha. Nobalola, olapara mbu bo ni tsisole tsing'enang'ena tsiomunyanza tsiasaalasibwa."
  76,20,"Ne nolenga eyo, olalola obwokholo nende obwaami obukhongo."
  76,21,"Hekulu wabu tsiliba tsingubo tsia Hariri (tsingwalafu) tsiobukondo bwamasafu, ne balifwala emikasa chieyifedha, ne Nyasaye wabu Omulesi alibanywesia eshinywebwa eshilafu muno."
  76,22,"(Alibaboolela mbu) “Toto kuno nikwo omurungo kwenyu, ne okhukhalabana khwenyu khufuchililwe.”"
  76,23,"Toto efwe khwakhwishilia Ikurani indutu, indutu."
  76,24,"Kho linda okhula shingala Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi alabusia eshina, ne olaulila yesiyesi mubo owetsimbi nohomba omukhayi tawe."
  76,25,"Ne itsulila elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nibushia nende nibwila."
  76,26,"Ne mushilo murerere obweni hasi, ne mutswenule oluwono olurambi lweshilo."
  76,27,"Toto Abandu bano bachama obulamu bwokhushialo, ne balekhanga inyuma wabu inyanga isiro."
  76,28,"Efwe khwabaloonga, ne nikhubaramwo amaani, ne nikhwenya, khunyala okhukalukhasia abandi bali shingabo."
  76,29,"Toto bwene kano ni ametsulisio. Kho, owenya, atiile injila itsia ewa Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  76,30,"Ne shimwakhenya tawe okhula Nyasaye achame. Toto bwene Nyasaye niye Omumanyi muno, Owamachesi po."
  76,31,"Yenjisinjia owayenya mutsimbabasi tsitsie, ne abamabii yabarecheshela eshinyasio eshilulu."
